                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for producing green methanol and green ammonia based on air gasification biomass and green hydrogen",
                    "一种基于空气气化生物质加绿氢生产绿甲醇和绿氨的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for producing green methanol and green ammonia based on air gasification biomass and green hydrogen, and particularly relates to the field of biomass energy utilization. A gasification furnace body is included, the exhaust end of the gasification furnace body is connected with the air inlet end of a dust removal heat exchanger through a pipeline, and the exhaust end of the dust removal heat exchanger is connected with a purification treatment box through a pipeline; the exhaust end of the purification treatment box is connected with a high-voltage electrostatic decoking device through a pipeline, the exhaust end of the high-voltage electrostatic decoking device is connected with an integration box, the exhaust end of the dust collection box is connected with a synthesis gas separator through a pipeline, and the two exhaust ends of the synthesis gas separator are connected with a first gas storage box and a second gas storage box respectively through pipelines; the first gas storage tank is connected with the first reactor through a pipeline, and the second gas storage tank is connected with the second reactor through a pipeline. Air is adopted as a gasifying agent, and compared with traditional oxygen, water vapor and carbon dioxide as gasifying agents, the cost is low."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于空气气化生物质加绿氢生产绿甲醇和绿氨的方法，具体涉及生物质能源利用领域，包括气化炉本体，所述气化炉本体的排气端通过管道连接除尘换热器的进气端，所述除尘换热器的排气端通过管道连接净化处理箱，所述净化处理箱的排气端通过管道连接高压静电除焦器，所述高压静电除焦器的排气端连接有集成箱，所述集尘箱的排气端通过管道连接合成气分离器，所述合成气分离器的两个排气端通过管道分别连接有第一储气箱和第二储气箱，所述第一储气箱通过管道连接第一反应器，所述第二储气箱通过管道连接第二反应器。本发明采用空气作为气化剂，相对于传统的氧气、水蒸气和二氧化碳作为气化剂成本较低。"
                }
            ]
